title: Trump Medical Treatment, Stimulus, 2020
itunes:title: Trump Medical Treatment, Stimulus, 2020
description:
Guests: Justin Sink, Bloomberg White House reporter, Dan David, Founder at Wolfpack Research, Drew Littman, Policy Director at Brownstein Hyatt Farber Schreck, and former Chief of Staff for Senator Al Franken, Brian Darling, former Senior Communications Director for Sen. Rand Paul and Founder of Liberty Government Affairs, and Michael Kinch, Director of the Centers for Research Innovation in Biotech and Drug Discovery at Washington University in St. Louis.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
